Create a function

FeatureData <- function(data) {
  features <- c(
                "Obesity" ,
                "Physical_Inactivity",
                "Access_Excercise",
                "Food_Env",
                "No_Collage_degree",   
                "Poverty",               
                "Diabetes",
                "X",
                "Y",
                "FIPS")
        fea <- data[,features]
        fea[, 1:6] = scale(fea[, 1:6])  # scale predictors
                return(fea)
                 }
df<-FeatureData(mf)

Merge with County Data

train.df <- merge(county,df, by='FIPS')

Distance matrix calculation

DM<-gw.dist(dp.locat=coordinates(train.df))

Bandwidth selection

bw.gwr <- bw.gwr(   Diabetes ~ 
                Obesity +
                Physical_Inactivity +
                Access_Excercise+
                Food_Env + 
                No_Collage_degree +    
                Poverty,       
                     data = train.df,
                     approach = "AICc",
                     kernel = "bisquare",
                     adaptive = TRUE,
                     dMat = DM)

Fit GW-RF Model

Coords<-df[ ,8:9]
grf.model <- grf(Diabetes ~ 
                Obesity +
                Physical_Inactivity +
                Access_Excercise+
                Food_Env + 
                No_Collage_degree +    
                Poverty,
            
            dframe=df, 
            bw=bw.gwr,           # nearest neighbors 
            mtry=4,              # Number of variables randomly sampled 
            ntree=2950,          # the number of trees to grow for each of the local random forests.
            kernel="adaptive",   # are "adaptive" or "fixed". 
            coords=df[ ,8:9],
            importance =T)

Local Model output

local.df<-mf[,1:3]
local.df$Obesity<-grf.model$Local.Pc.IncMSE$Obesity
local.df$Physical_Inactivity<-grf.model$Local.Pc.IncMSE$Physical_Inactivity
local.df$Access_Excercise<-grf.model$Local.Pc.IncMSE$Access_Excercise
local.df$Food_Env<-grf.model$Local.Pc.IncMSE$Food_Env
local.df$Poverty<-grf.model$Local.Pc.IncMSE$Poverty
local.df$No_Collage_degree<-grf.model$Local.Pc.IncMSE$No_Collage_degree
local.df$local.res<-grf.model$LGofFit$LM_ResPred
local.df$local.R2<-grf.model$LGofFit$LM_Rsq100
local.df$local.MSE<-grf.model$LGofFit$LM_MSR
local.df$local.pred<-grf.model$LGofFit$LM_yfitPred
local.df$global.pred<-grf.model$Global.Model$predicted

write.csv(local.df, "Local_model_outPut.csv", row.names=F)
local.SPDF <- merge(county,local.df, by='FIPS')
names(local.SPDF)

Map Local IncMSE

col.palette.IncMSE<-colorRampPalette(c("grey95", "sky blue", "palegreen","yellow","wheat2", "salmon","red"),space="rgb",interpolate = "linear")

p.Local_IncMSE <-spplot(local.SPDF ,
                 c(
                     "Poverty",
                     "No_Collage_degree",
                      
                     "Access_Excercise",
                     "Food_Env",
                      
                     "Obesity",
                     "Physical_Inactivity" 
                      ),         
           
                names.attr = c(
         
                     "(e) Poverty", 
                     "(f) Education",
                    
                     "(c) Access to exercise",
                     "(d) Food environment index", 
                     
                     "(a) Adult obesity",
                     "(b) Physical inactivity"),
           layout=c(2, 3),
           par.strip.text=list(cex=1.25, lines=2, col="black"),
           main = "",
           between = list(x = 1.5, y = 2),
           sp.layout=list(points,labels,state,div),
           par.settings=list(strip.background=list(col="transparent"),
                             strip.border = list(col = 'grey95',lwd=0.5),
                             axis.line=list(col="grey95",lwd=0.5)),
           col="grey95",
           colorkey=list(space="right",height=1, width=2,labels=list(cex=1.85)),
           col.regions=col.palette.IncMSE(100))                         


windows(width=9, height=10)
tiff( file="FIG_MAPS_Local_IncMSE.tif", 
      width=9, height=10, units = "in", pointsize = 12, res=900,
      restoreConsole = T,bg="transparent")
print(p.Local_IncMSE )
dev.off()
